description: NK star Shane Erickson fights newcomer Christian Wilde. Shane shows up under the weather but he decides to soldier on. First time on NK, Christian Wilde is a bad-ass but he's a smoker. Smokers get winded fast on NK. Two hot studs are ready to fight but each has his own issue. Regardless, one will be the other one's bitch for the day.
title: Shane Erickson vs Christian Wilde The Oil Match
